260
00:12:28.498 --> 00:12:31.917
Carla. I'm really sorry. I'll give you
all your patients back. I didn't mean to--

261
00:12:35.463 --> 00:12:39.968
<i>Oh. no. She's Dominican mad.
I wonder what</i> "testiculos" <i>means.</i>

262
00:12:40.593 --> 00:12:43.512
Okay. Manny. how are we...
Oh. dude. come on!

263
00:12:43.513 --> 00:12:45.598
You gotta be kidding me.
We talked about this.

264
