269
00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:04.701
You know. Manny.
I get the connection to grandmas.

270
00:13:05.952 --> 00:13:11.623
I remember having <i>pollo</i> and plantains
with my <i>abuela</i> and her <i>testiculos</i>.

271
00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:12.917
<i>Nope. that felt wrong.</i>

272
00:13:13.459 --> 00:13:14.711
I'll be back.

273
00:13:21.843 --> 00:13:24.219
