284
00:13:49.370 --> 00:13:52.706
Totally. Well. except a little fun.
I'll see you later. then?

285
00:13:52.707 --> 00:13:55.375
Yeah. or maybe you won't. I don't care.

286
00:13:55.376 --> 00:13:57.128
