Look. I know it's hard to say goodbye...

288
00:14:08.598 --> 00:14:09.599
Goodbye.

289
00:14:14.353 --> 00:14:17.940
You know what? Go ahead. be mad.
I don't care anymore.

290
00:14:20.068 --> 00:14:24.155
