But it was always fun.

313
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:31.389
Now...

314
00:15:33.182 --> 00:15:36.185
it's just hard. I can't keep up.

315
00:15:37.019 --> 00:15:38.146
Finally.

316
00:15:39.730 --> 00:15:42.399
- Interesting choice of last words.
- I should finish.

317
00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:46.279
You've always been smarter than me.
stronger than me.

318
