you actually need me.

320
00:15:56.497 --> 00:15:58.249
And I get to be there for you.

321
00:15:59.083 --> 00:16:00.334
I love you.

322
00:16:00.918 --> 00:16:02.170
I know.

323
00:16:04.338 --> 00:16:05.839
Okay. get off me. I'm hot.

324
00:16:05.840 --> 00:16:08.425
You guys will always have each other.
and I'm super happy.

325
00:16:08.426 --> 00:16:10.260
but I just want to remind you
that I might die alone.

326
