332
00:16:28.237 --> 00:16:31.741
<i>And there it was.
the slippery slope of kindness.</i>

333
00:16:32.491 --> 00:16:33.951
I hope they come too.

334
00:16:34.911 --> 00:16:36.411
Maybe if I put on a concert.

335
00:16:36.412 --> 00:16:39.081
